    "description":  "Staying on top of finances is vital for small companies. \r\n\r\nA good accountant can help you do this and more. ",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003eHelp us to improve the director information hub by \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.smartsurvey.co.uk/s/PCI2DV/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ecompleting a short feedback survey.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-are-the-benefits-of-having-an-accountant\"\u003eWhat are the benefits of having an accountant?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"saves-time\"\u003eSaves time\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn accountant can save you time to help you concentrate on the core business of your company.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"saves-money\"\u003eSaves money\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn accountant can help when it comes to paying income tax, National Insurance contributions, Corporation Tax and VAT, as well as filing annual accounts on time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis can avoid expensive \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/penalty-points-and-penalties-if-you-submit-your-vat-return-late\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003epenalties and fines\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"uncomplicates-the-complicated\"\u003eUncomplicates the complicated\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTax can be complicated. A good accountant will work with you to understand the difficult aspects of taxation like IR35 and annual tax computations and deal with HMRC and Companies House on your behalf.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"grow-your-business\"\u003eGrow your business\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA good accountant can be a source of guidance and, in some circumstances, advice. If they are experienced, they could be a valuable asset for you as a director.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"help-in-difficult-times\"\u003eHelp in difficult times\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are experiencing financial difficulty or even if you are not, accountants can help you in a number of ways such as monitoring your cashflow and flagging up signs of distress early.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"finding-an-accountant\"\u003eFinding an accountant\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBefore you employ the services of an accountant or tax agent, make sure they are qualified to do the work you want them to do.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou should read fully the terms of engagement an accountant will provide you with before they undertaking any work on your behalf.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-choose-a-tax-agent\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eHow to choose a tax agent\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/appoint-tax-agent\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eAppoint a tax agent\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub-help-and-guidance-resources\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eFind an accountant\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGo back to the director information hub homepage.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
